name: Super Crunch Box
details:
Marshall in a box ( MIAB ) style pedalThe MI Effects Crunch Box has become a modern-day classic that has garnered a loyal army of fans. We have re-designed the original and added new features like external PRESENCE control, COMP switch and LO/HI gain modes that now makes the Super Crunch Box the authority on British amp distortion for any era!
